snippet.title: Mission Raniganj - The Great Bharat Rescue | Official Teaser | Akshay Kumar | In Cinemas 6th October
snippet.description:
MISSION RANIGANJ - The Great Bharat Rescue is inspired by a real-life hero, Late Jaswant Singh Gill, an engineer who led a challenging rescue mission to save trapped miners from a flooded coal mine. This edge-of-the-seat thriller highlights Gill's courage and relentless efforts, showcasing his resilience to overcome adversities. A race against time rescue mission starring Akshay Kumar and Parineeti Chopra in the lead with a talented ensemble cast - Kumund Mishra, Rajesh Sharma, Pavan Malhotra, Ravi Kishan, Dibyendu Bhattacharya and Varun Badola to name a few.

Watch the story of Bharat‚Äôs true hero with #MissionRaniganj in cinemas on 6th October.

snippet.title: Fastest TVS Bike - Apache RTR 310  | First Look
snippet.description: Here's everything you need to know about the new 2023 TVS Apache RTR 310 that has been launched at a starting price of Rs 2.43 lacs, whereas the top-end variant costs Rs 2.64 lacs (ex-showroom) The vehicle is available in three different colours - Yellow, Black and a special Blue. Though it shares its frame with the RR310 and BMW G310 R, the company has added a new aluminium sub-frame to lower its weight and has re-worked on its engine to make it faster and more powerful.

snippet.title: 4th T20I | Highlights | New Zealand Tour Of England | 5th September 2023
snippet.description:
In the 4th and final T20I, England batted first and reached a competitive total of 175 runs on the scoreboard. Jonny Bairstow led the batting with a powerful knock of 73 runs. New Zealand however showcased an excellent batting performance and chased down the target in just 17.2 overs and levelled the series 2 - 2.
.

Episode 3870: Emergency Society Meeting
--------------------------------------------------------
At Gokuldham Society, everyone is looking forward to the Janmashtami celebrations. Anjali, Babita, and Komal discuss their specially created festive sweet delights. Abdul enters and announces that Bhide has called an emergency meeting for tonight to discuss the "Dahi Handi" ritual. Later, Madhvi enters and explains the cause of Bhide's urgent meeting. The wish-granting matka (earthen pot) presented by Tapu Sena Gor by a spiritual leader piques the interest of all the women. Popatlal accuses Bhide and Abdul of failing to inform him about the mystical matka. Everyone in Gokuldham is looking forward to Bhide's meeting and his announcement regarding the chosen one.

snippet.title: Launch of PSLV-C57/Aditya-L1 Mission from Satish Dhawan Space Centre (SDSC) SHAR, Sriharikota
snippet.description: Aditya L1 shall be the first space based Indian mission to study the Sun. The spacecraft shall be placed in a halo orbit around the Lagrange point 1 (L1) of the Sun-Earth system, which is about 1.5 million km from the Earth. A satellite placed in the halo orbit around the L1 point has the major advantage of continuously viewing the Sun without any occultation/eclipses. This will provide a greater advantage of observing the solar activities and its effect on space weather in real time.

Episode 3869: Iccha Purti  Matki
--------------------------------------------------------
A saint visits the temple of the Gokuldham Society and presents Tapu Sena an Iccha Purti Matki, promising to grant the wishes of whoever breaks it on Janmashtami. Tapu Sena, who was busy in the preparation for Krishna Janmotsav finds it odd. Goli wishes for ladoos from the Iccha Purti Matki, Sonu tells them about the words of the saint about breaking the pot at dahi handi. Tapu Sena takes the Iccha Purti Matki to Bapuji and narrates the whole incident to him. Watch the episode.

snippet.description:
Brace yourselves as we present to you the action-packed trailer of #Jawan. Directed by Atlee, the film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance). The film is set to release in cinemas on September 7, 2023 - in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 37 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 5th September 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet.
